summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2206, for the improvement of Republican Street, from 5th Avenue North to Nob Hill Avenue, and of Nob Hill Avenue, from Republican Street to Harrison Street; all in the City of Seattle, by planking the same 16 feet in width; under Ordinance No. 22194 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
